{"tid":661293,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2018 荷里活片酬排行榜 TOP.10，第一名的賺進 1.9 億多港幣！","createTime":"2018-05-11T12:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T14:32:28.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48fc9e6ccc8f2317f29f24757df5b4f0d6ddd620","tid":661293,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"美國影視雜誌《Variety》，針對 2018 年荷里活的影星們統計出一個片酬排行榜，其中入圍的女性只有三位。<br />\n<br />\n10. Leonardo Dicaprio 《Once Upon a Time In Hollywood》(2019) &ndash; 1000 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc3da1360.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc3da1360.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=d71f66fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. Sandra Bullock 《Minions》 (2015) &ndash; 1000 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc63b8f69.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc63b8f69.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=95ae738b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. Harisson Ford 《Indiana Jones 5》 (2020) &ndash; 1000 到 1200 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c39c0e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c39c0e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=f69d72d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. Tom Cruise 《The Mummy》 (2017) &ndash; 1100 到 1300 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c3799f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c3799f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=608ddaec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Seth Rogen 《Flarsky》(2019) &ndash; 1500 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c1eefe.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c1eefe.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=a877b35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. Jennifer Lawrence 《Red Sparrow》(2018) &ndash; 1500 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c264e1.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c264e1.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=9be563a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. Anne Hathaway 《Barbie》 (2020) &ndash; 1500 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c2573a.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c2573a.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=f507b542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. Vin Diesel 《The Fate of the Furious 8》 (2017) &ndash; 2000 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c19013.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c19013.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=ff18db55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.巨石強森（Dwayne Johnson）《Red Notice》 (2020) &ndash; 2200 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinabaike.com/uploads/allimg/101205/2300225G4-0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinabaike.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F101205%2F2300225G4-0.jpg&h=844e81a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Daniel Craig 《007》（Bond 25） (2019) &ndash; 2500 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/78364/5af3bc0c13d5a.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F78364%2F5af3bc0c13d5a.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=3fa010f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光看這些片酬就相當驚人，多次表達不再續演《007》系列電影的 Daniel Craig，也難敵 2500 萬美金片酬的誘惑，即將再度演出，真是太厲害。"},{"pid":"3368746e0a07cfbe7faedccee1b5b6ff6de3691a","tid":661293,"uid":38911,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"巨石笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd521cea7cba2526da535ad38a582eb1df96b972","tid":661293,"uid":133502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821eaf948eecb9fa8d3c466b82268b06b66613e5","tid":661293,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01be46b2fbc9ecf0ebe9852a2a753311fd68194f","tid":661293,"uid":73765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"真係巨石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb40689869c33ac4e01b21df9c68e6b3b75f7f7d","tid":661293,"uid":83805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"睇到巨石笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}